# ── APIClient fork: scratch + regenerable artifacts ──────────────────
# The forced-execution work generates many throwaway fixtures, capture
# dumps, and rebuildable wasm. None belong in history. The polarity
# scenarios were MOVED to APIClient `testing/fixtures/*.html` (the
# approved HTML form, served + visited live); the fork tracks NO `_*`
# fixtures — see the "Fork version-control system" section in
# APIClient/CLAUDE.md.
